The **~AllPages** [[Help:WikiPlugin|plugin]] lists all pages in this wiki.

== Usage
{{{
<<AllPages arguments>>
}}}

== Arguments

All [[Help:PageList|PageList]] arguments, plus the following ones.

{| class="bordered"
|-
! Argument
! Description
! Default value
|-
| **noheader**
| Boolean header should be omitted.
| false
|-
| **include_empty**
| Boolean
| false
|-
| **info**
|
| none
|}

== Example

{{{
<<AllPages limit=20 cols=3>>
}}}

<<AllPages  limit=20 cols=3>>

